item.title: CVE-2023-1547|2023-07-26T09:02:48.423Z -- elra -- parkmatik
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection') vulnerability in Elra Parkmatik allows SQL Injection through SOAP Parameter Tampering, Command Line Execution through SQL Injection.This issue affects Parkmatik: before 02.01-a51.
